{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7a13899937","title":"毛泽东和袁水拍、臧克家的谈话(摘录)","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"969f693f49","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"7a13899937"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a6b8d2b91a","type":"title","text":"毛泽东和袁水拍、臧克家的谈话(摘录)","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937"},{"id":"ebc298d02e","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937"},{"id":"f3259124ee","type":"paragraph","text":"你们看，将来即使革命在全世界都得到胜利之后，会不会还有斗争？","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937"},{"id":"37209014f0","type":"paragraph","text":"(答：说不上来。)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937"},{"id":"1fd82e3c16","type":"paragraph","text":"我看是会有的，领导与被领导(群众)之间，总是会有矛盾斗争的。不过斗争的武器不是枪杆子，而是笔杆子，在墙上写大字报。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937"},{"id":"f066f42752","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937"},{"id":"f94da256de","type":"paragraph","text":"我自己写一点旧体诗词。象词，很短小，这种形式运用起来方便，也就熟悉了。他们给我弄了一部“诗综”，我看李攀龙的诗，有的很好。杜甫的诗，有好的，大多数并不怎么样。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937"},{"id":"011a370637","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937"},{"id":"196966edc7","type":"paragraph","text":"民歌最早是四言的多，象《诗经》，后来发展成五、七言，现在七言的比较多。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937"},{"id":"c2a81af727","type":"paragraph","text":"我看新诗应该写得“精炼，大体整齐，押大体相近的韵”，可以专为新诗编一部《新诗韵》。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937"}],"page":{"id":"5d39223484","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a13899937","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}